        <item>
            <title>Version 2.0.18</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;">Release Notes for Version 2.0.18</h3>
                <ul style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <li><b>Rich Markdown Engine:</b> Introduced a powerful new web-based markdown renderer for notes, offering beautifully formatted text and drastically improved performance.</li>
    <li><b>Advanced Diagrams:</b> Automatically render <code>dbml</code>, <code>mermaid</code>, <code>dot</code>, and <code>graphviz</code> diagrams directly inline with your notes.</li>
    <li><b>Source View Toggle:</b> Easily flip between your rendered diagrams and their raw source code with a single click using the new <b>&lt;/&gt; Source</b> button.</li>
    <li><b>Syntax Highlighting:</b> Enjoy beautiful code formatting for all programming languages using the premium Atom One Dark theme.</li>
    <li><b>Math Support:</b> Native rendering of mathematical equations and formulas using KaTeX.</li>
    <li><b>Performance:</b> Optimized markdown rendering layout and robust local-scheme handling for better stability and smoother scrolling.</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
